<h1 class="firstHeading" id="firstHeading" lang="en">2001–02 UEFA Cup</h1>
<div class="mw-body-content" id="bodyContent">
<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>

</td>
</tr>
</table>
<p>The <b>2001–02 UEFA Cup</b> was won by <a href="/wiki/Feyenoord" title="Feyenoord">Feyenoord</a> at their home ground in the final against <a href="/wiki/Borussia_Dortmund" title="Borussia Dortmund">Borussia Dortmund</a>. It was the second time they won the competition.</p>
<p></p>

<p></p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Association_team_allocation">Association team allocation</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=2001%E2%80%9302_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Association team allocation">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<p>A total of 146 teams from 51 <a href="/wiki/UEFA" title="UEFA">UEFA</a> associations participated in the 2001–02 UEFA Cup. Associations are allocated places according to their 2000 <a href="/wiki/UEFA_coefficient#League_coefficient" title="UEFA coefficient">UEFA league coefficient</a>.<sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-1"><a href="#cite_note-1">[1]</a></sup></p>
<p>Below is the qualification scheme for the 2001–02 UEFA Cup:</p>
<ul>
<li>Associations 1–6 each enter three teams</li>
<li>Associations 7–8 each enter four teams</li>
<li>Associations 9–15 each enter two teams</li>
<li>Associations 16–21 each enter three teams</li>
<li>Associations 22–49 each enter two teams, with the exception of Liechtenstein who enter one.</li>
<li>Associations 50-51 each enter one team</li>
<li>The top three associations of the 2000–2001 <a class="mw-redirect" href="/wiki/UEFA_Fair_Play_ranking" title="UEFA Fair Play ranking">UEFA Fair Play ranking</a> each gain an additional berth</li>
<li>16 teams eliminated from the <a href="/wiki/2001%E2%80%9302_UEFA_Champions_League_qualifying_rounds#Third_qualifying_round" title="2001–02 UEFA Champions League qualifying rounds">2001–02 UEFA Champions League qualifying rounds</a></li>
<li>8 teams eliminated from the <a href="/wiki/2001%E2%80%9302_UEFA_Champions_League_group_stage" title="2001–02 UEFA Champions League group stage">2001–02 UEFA Champions League group stage</a> are transferred to the UEFA Cup</li>
<li>3 winners of the <a href="/wiki/2001_UEFA_Intertoto_Cup" title="2001 UEFA Intertoto Cup">Intertoto Cup</a></li>
<li>The winner of the <a href="/wiki/2000%E2%80%9301_UEFA_Cup" title="2000–01 UEFA Cup">2000–01 UEFA Cup</a></li>
</ul>

<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Distribution">Distribution</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=2001%E2%80%9302_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="Edit section: Distribution">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>

<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Redistribution_rules">Redistribution rules</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=2001%E2%80%9302_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: Redistribution rules">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<p>A UEFA Cup place is vacated when a team qualify for both the Champions League and the UEFA Cup, or qualify for the UEFA Cup by more than one method. When a place is vacated, it is redistributed within the national association by the following rules:&lt;</p>
<ul>
<li>When the domestic cup winners (considered as the "highest-placed" qualifier within the national association) also qualify for the Champions League, their UEFA Cup place is vacated, and the remaining UEFA Cup qualifiers are moved up one place, with the final place (with the earliest starting round) taken by the domestic cup runners-up, provided they do not already qualify for the Champions League or the UEFA Cup. Otherwise, this place is taken by the highest-placed league finisher which do not qualify for the UEFA Cup yet.</li>
<li>When the domestic cup winners also qualify for the UEFA Cup through league position, their place through the league position is vacated, and the UEFA Cup qualifiers which finish lower in the league are moved up one place, with the final place taken by the highest-placed league finisher which do not qualify for the UEFA Cup yet.</li>
<li>A place vacated by the League Cup winners is taken by the highest-placed league finisher which do not qualify for the UEFA Cup yet.</li>
<li>A Fair Play place is taken by the highest-ranked team in the domestic Fair Play table which do not qualify for the Champions League or UEFA Cup yet.</li>
</ul>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Teams">Teams</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=2001%E2%80%9302_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5" title="Edit section: Teams">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<p>The labels in the parentheses show how each team qualified for the place of its starting round:</p>
<ul>
<li>CW: Cup winners</li>
<li>CR: Cup runners-up</li>
<li>LC: League Cup winners</li>
<li>Nth: League position</li>
<li>P-W: End-of-season European competition play-off winners</li>
<li>FP: Fair play</li>
<li>IT: Intertoto Cup winners</li>
<li>UCL: Relegated from the Champions League
<ul>
<li>GS: Third-placed teams from the group stage</li>
<li>Q3: Losers from the third qualifying round</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>

<p><span id="1"></span><sup>1</sup> Only one leg was played, in a neutral venue in Warsaw, Poland, due to security concerns in Russia.</p>
<p><span id="2"></span><sup>2</sup> PSG won 3–0 because there was a blackout in <a href="/wiki/Bucharest" title="Bucharest">Bucharest</a> at that time and the match was stopped immediately in favour of the visitors.</p>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="First_leg_2">First leg</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=2001%E2%80%9302_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Edit section: First leg">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>

<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Second_leg_2">Second leg</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=2001%E2%80%9302_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: Second leg">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>

</div>
<p><i>Helsingborg won 3–3 on aggregate after away goals.</i></p>

<p><span id="Milan_v_CSKA_Sofia"></span></p>
<div class="vevent" style="width: 100%; background-color: transparent; clear:both">

<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Second_leg_3">Second leg</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=2001%E2%80%9302_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14" title="Edit section: Second leg">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>

<p><span class="summary" style="display: none;"><a class="mw-redirect" href="/wiki/Parma_F.C." title="Parma F.C.">Parma</a> <span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Italy" title="Italy"><img alt="Italy" class="thumbborder" data-file-height="1000" data-file-width="1500" height="15" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/03/Flag_of_Italy.svg/23px-Flag_of_Italy.svg.png" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/03/Flag_of_Italy.svg/35px-Flag_of_Italy.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/03/Flag_of_Italy.svg/45px-Flag_of_Italy.svg.png 2x" width="23"/></a></span> v <span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Netherlands" title="Netherlands"><img alt="Netherlands" class="thumbborder" data-file-height="600" data-file-width="900" height="15" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/20/Flag_of_the_Netherlands.svg/23px-Flag_of_the_Netherlands.svg.png" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/20/Flag_of_the_Netherlands.svg/35px-Flag_of_the_Netherlands.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/20/Flag_of_the_Netherlands.svg/45px-Flag_of_the_Netherlands.svg.png 2x" width="23"/></a></span> <a href="/wiki/FC_Utrecht" title="FC Utrecht">Utrecht</a></span></p>

<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="First_leg_4">First leg</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=2001%E2%80%9302_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16" title="Edit section: First leg">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>

<p><i>Rangers 0–0 Paris Saint-Germain on aggregate. Rangers won 4–3 on penalties.</i></p>

<td style="vertical-align:top;text-align:right;">19:30</td>

<p><i>Club Brugge 4–4 Lyon on aggregate. Lyon won on away goals.</i></p>

<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Second_leg_5">Second leg</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=2001%E2%80%9302_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=20" title="Edit section: Second leg">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>

<p><i>Milan 1–1 Roda JC on aggregate. Milan won 3–2 on penalties.</i></p>

<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Second_leg_6">Second leg</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=2001%E2%80%9302_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=23" title="Edit section: Second leg">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>

<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="First_leg_7">First leg</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=2001%E2%80%9302_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=25" title="Edit section: First leg">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>

<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Second_leg_7">Second leg</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=2001%E2%80%9302_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=26" title="Edit section: Second leg">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<div class="vevent" style="width: 100%; background-color: transparent; clear:both">

<p><i>Borussia Dortmund won 5–3 on aggregate.</i></p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Final">Final</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=2001%E2%80%9302_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=27" title="Edit section: Final">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<div class="hatnote" role="note">Main article: <a href="/wiki/2002_UEFA_Cup_Final" title="2002 UEFA Cup Final">2002 UEFA Cup Final</a></div>

<th class="navbox-group" scope="row">League cups</th>
<td class="navbox-list navbox-odd hlist" style="text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
